>> POX

	https://github.com/noxrepo/pox
	https://github.com/noxrepo/pox/blob/gar-experimental/pox/misc/ip_loadbalancer.py
	https://noxrepo.github.io/pox-doc/html/
	
	install: clone/donwload repo
	
	./pox.py log.level --DEBUG filename

>> MININET

	https://github.com/mininet/mininet/wiki/Introduction-to-mininet
	
	install: sudo apt install mininet
	
>> MINIEDIT
	
	install: https://github.com/mininet/mininet
	
	1. go to example folder inside mininet in terminal
	2. run the following cmd
		sudo python miniedit.py
	
	
>> HOW TO RUN CODE WITH MININET

	1. ./pox.py log.level --DEBUG filename.py --ip=10.0.1.1 --servers=ip1,ip2
	2. sudo mn --topo single,6 --mac --arp --controller=remote
	3. xterm h1 h2 h3 ....
	4. from xterm run the servers
		python -m SimpleHTTPServer 80
	5. do load test from any one host
		ab -n 100 -c 10 -g test.csv http://10.0.1.1/

>> HOW TO RUN CODE WITH MINIEDIT
	
	1. ./pox.py log.level --DEBUG filename.py --ip=10.0.1.1 --servers=ip1,ip2
	2. sudo python miniedit.py
	3. create topology in miniedit
	4. enable cli ( goto edit in toolbar/preferences)
	5. run the topology by clicking run in toolbar
	5. POX CONTROLLER COMMANDS : ( open 4 terminals for 4 different algo's)
		5.1 rand : ./pox.py log.level --DEBUG rand --ip=10.1.0.0 --servers=10.1.1.1,10.1.1.2,10.1.1.3
		5.2 rounds :./pox.py log.level --DEBUG round --ip=10.1.0.0 --servers=10.1.2.1,10.1.2.2,10.1.2.3 openflow.of_01 --port=6634
		5.3 round :./pox.py log.level --DEBUG least --ip=10.1.0.0 --servers=10.1.3.1,10.1.3.2,10.1.3.3 openflow.of_01 --port=6635
		5.4 W Round : ./pox.py log.level --DEBUG wrr --ip=10.1.0.0 --servers=10.1.4.1:1,10.1.4.2:2,10.1.4.3:3 openflow.of_01 --port=6636
	6. Single topo:
		./pox.py log.level --DEBUG rand --ip=10.0.1.1 --servers=10.0.0.1,10.0.0.2,10.0.0.3,10.0.0.4,10.0.0.5,10.0.0.6,10.0.0.7,10.0.0.8,10.0.0.9,10.0.0.10,10.0.0.11,10.0.0.12


